DIA_ROLF_EXIT_03_02: P-p-please, let's hurry! I can't stay he-here any longer!
DIA_ROLF_EXIT_15_02: Wait, wait, what about the gold?
DIA_ROLF_EXIT_03_03: Yeah, r-right. H-here, that's all I have.
DIA_Rolf_SQ109_Hello_03_03: May I-Innos reward you with children! I thought I was d-done f-f-for!
DIA_Rolf_SQ109_Hello_15_04: You have nothing to fear anymore.
DIA_Rolf_SQ109_Hello_HowLong_15_01: How long have you been here?

DIA_Rolf_SQ109_Hello_GiveMeGold_03_02: Y-yes... of course. M-my whole paycheck. As soon as I'm down, y-you'll get it.
